<script>
export default {
  RevenueChart: {
    series: [
      {
        name: "2015",
        data: [
          800000,
          1200000,
          1400000,
          1300000,
          1200000,
          1400000,
          1300000,
          1300000,
          1200000
        ]
      },
      {
        name: "2020",
        data: [
          200000,
          400000,
          500000,
          300000,
          400000,
          500000,
          300000,
          300000,
          400000
        ]
      },
      {
        name: "2025",
        data: [
          100000,
          200000,
          400000,
          600000,
          200000,
          400000,
          600000,
          600000,
          200000
        ]
      }
    ],
    chartOptions: {
      grid: {
        show: true,
        borderColor: "rgba(0, 0, 0, .3)",
        strokeDashArray: 3,
        padding: {
          left: 0,
          right: 0,
          bottom: 0
        }
      },
      plotOptions: {
        bar: {
          horizontal: false,
          columnWidth: "15%",
          endingShape: "flat"
        }
      },
      colors: ["#1e88e5", "#26c6da", "#fc4b6c"],
      fill: {
        type: "solid",
        opacity: 1
      },
      chart: {
        stacked: true,
        toolbar: {
          show: false
        },
        sparkline: {
          enabled: false
        }
      },
      dataLabels: {
        enabled: false
      },
      markers: {
        size: 0
      },
      legend: {
        show: false
      },
      xaxis: {
        type: "category",
        categories: [
          "Jan",
          "Feb",
          "Mar",
          "Apr",
          "May",
          "Jun",
          "Jul",
          "Aug",
          "Sept"
        ],
        labels: {
          style: {
            cssClass: "text-muted fill-color"
          }
        }
      },
      yaxis: {
        show: true,
        labels: {
          style: {
            cssClass: "text-muted fill-color"
          }
        }
      },
      stroke: {
        curve: "straight",
        width: 0
      },
      tooltip: {
        theme: "dark"
      }
    }
  }
};
</script>
